text: Hitler Nababan (born 1964) is an Indonesian politician from the Democratic Party. He was a member of the Karawang Regional People's Representative Council (the city's legislative body) from 2014 until 2019. He was born in 1964, moved to Karawang in 1994. Before he was a member of parliament, he worked as a moneylender. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Democratic Party (Indonesia) politicians Category:Batak people
